{"tid":1062401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士客投訴車廂冇清潔　九巴「鬧客」反獲激讚？","createTime":"2019-03-15T05:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T16:19:03.000Z","uid":225464,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"93ffef1ce335851c5f4974ce6a122d8ba0a9b404","tid":1062401,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:23:24.000Z","msg":"<strong>巴士客投訴車廂冇清潔 九巴「鬧客」反獲激讚？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2FcM4yt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2FcM4yt&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=b0445855\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2FcM4yt</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190315/photo/bkn-20190315123730996-0315_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190315131731\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190315%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190315123730996-0315_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190315131731&h=48d51845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部分乘客欠公德心？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公關災難定神回覆？近日九龍巴士公司在Facebook專頁宣傳新型巴士，被網民諷刺車廂日常衞生欠佳，惟九巴專頁小編的一句「鬥嘴」，竟吸引逾5000個讚好，到底他說了甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n有網民在九巴專頁留言批評，即使九巴推出新型巴士，亦是「表面風光」︰「新又點？都冇人清潔嘅」。未料九巴小編回覆︰「清潔又點？都無公德心嘅。」、「我哋當然有清潔啦。如果冇清潔，真係不堪設想」。<br />\n<br />\n一眾網友大食花生，有網友質疑︰「公關發晦氣」、「咁答人嘢好不知所謂喎」、「佢係咪入錯帳號嚟回應」。<br />\n<br />\n但不少網民則大撐九巴：「佢講事實」、「垃圾根本就係乘客帶上車」、「10蚊8蚊搭轉車，你想每轉車有人全車抹一次呀」、「都唔明點解啲人唔自己帶走垃圾，垃圾放入垃圾桶原來啲人係唔X識㗎」。"},{"pid":"f328db4fc741bf857cf434db25e1e88bf9585fdb","tid":1062401,"uid":189528,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:35:43.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成個麥當勞餐又真係過份"},{"pid":"69d4daae52bf72caab9af58dce21865897f7d16e","tid":1062401,"uid":48947,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:39:31.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n好撚多仆街冚家產食完野唔清潔<br />\n見過有人撩完鼻屎抆落啲位度<br />\n我屌你老母搭熱狗嗰時都無咁撚污糟<br />\n依幾年真係每況愈下"},{"pid":"cb3f1a5f9a46001e286545ff2ccfa12068359244","tid":1062401,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f328db4fc741bf857cf434db25e1e88bf9585fdb","tid":1062401,"uid":189528,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:35:43.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成個麥當勞餐又真係過份"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T07:59:45.000Z","msg":"真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54de4bc1c9c954454ce760d715d4276087c210aa","tid":1062401,"uid":3668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T08:01:26.000Z","msg":"成堆死老野一上車就係度剪指甲啦 根本自己都冇品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeaf816223f3eab668c54a52c55f82c95107b050","tid":1062401,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69d4daae52bf72caab9af58dce21865897f7d16e","tid":1062401,"uid":48947,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:39:31.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n好撚多仆街冚家產食完野唔清潔<br />\n見過有人撩完鼻屎抆落啲位度<br />\n我屌你老母搭熱狗嗰時都無咁撚污糟<br />\n依幾年真係每況愈下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T08:01:52.000Z","msg":"上個月有單仲誇張<br />\n有強國人抆鼻屎落隔離乘客 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8690724735df1e405eda3042ccceff7409838e05","tid":1062401,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T08:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f31fc312195963dafe115bdf7e479924b62265","tid":1062401,"uid":76437,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T08:02:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4dd2693a7c08dfe2e73bed11e7160dca43cba951","tid":1062401,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T08:05:20.000Z","msg":"擺報紙果d又係仆街黎 一拎開佢又整污糟隻手"},{"pid":"827065e230a7c728e0ba0000e170f9310a2a58a2","tid":1062401,"uid":99856,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T08:07:49.000Z","msg":"越多支那人坐既車 越污糟"},{"pid":"4094c4e3f048f1c80d2d82b2ce84fd8b60132781","tid":1